reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 22, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Easy to assemble and hang. I just love them and they look so beautiful. I'm very happy with my purchase. Good price and excellent quality.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 18, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect addition to new bathroom
reviews.reviewText: I love this pair of lights/decor! The lights are just the right amount of "flash" and the look is perfect. I have them in our newly renovated bathroom. These make the perfect amount of accent light. It works as a little "nightlight" or just a decor accent. The timer on the remote is a big plus. While guests are over we can have the lights on for the right amount of time and don't have to worry about forgetting to turn them off. The flowers are a little more of a cream color, but still fantastic and very pretty. They are fake, yes. But they complete the look of this item well. I will be able to easily switch out the flowers for different colors during the holidays, then put the original right back in. The battery pack sits in a specific are on the back of the wooden design, out of sight. Easy to swap the batteries when needed. These sconces would look good in any room of the house! Great value, great item and I would recommend them!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This isn't super heavy but you do want to secure it very well, especially if you are hanging it in a place with humidity.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love the look
reviews.reviewText: Really pretty and easy to use. Soft fairy lights look nice in any room.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 23, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Better on person!
reviews.reviewText: I love these! I somehow overlooked the fact that there are two in each purchase, so I ordered two sets! One of the sets has a remote that doesn't work at all, so I'm taking off a star for that dissatisfaction. The remote is needed to set the timer, so, luckily, my mistake gave me two remotes, and the other one does work. I would've had to contact the company or exchange the product, if I didn't get a working remote. I like that I can choose a 2, 4, 6, or 8 hour timer.These sconces are more beautiful in person! I ordered the grey, and they have the rustic wood look that I love!I purchased navy, hydrangea flowers from Amazon, and added one bunch to each jar, to match my decor. A couple of the cream flowers, which come with this item, fell off, while assembling, but they are very easy to put back on.The lights add a nice, nighttime ambiance to the bathroom, and provide enough lighting to see while using the room. A couple of the settings are similar. There are a couple of strobe settings, which I hate, and could be a concern for anyone prone to seizures. It's great to have a permanent on option, also.Overall, the sconces are classy, rustic, farmhouse decor. Even though I originally only wanted 2 sconces, I'm keeping the four that I purchased! These are giftable (assuming the remote works).

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 18, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Ive ordered these a few times. They make a perfect gift. They are exactly as shown. The lights make it even better. Make sure you have batteries since not included. Look really cute in a bathroom or to complete a picture collage wall.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Prefect decor for the bathroom
reviews.reviewText: Bought these for our bathroom decor. They are PREFECT! The lights have setting for whennyou want them to shut off, has multiple settings for lights display, brightness adjustment, we actually use this for a night light. The high brightness is so bright, you don't even need to turn the bathroom light on. Ha ha

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cutest little lamps!
reviews.reviewText: I bought these a while ago but they have made the most cutest wall lamps! I absolutely adore them and have changed out the flowers for the seasons! Would absolutely buy again!
These were really easy to assemble and really well made! The quality is really really nice for the price, well worth it!

Love them. The timer works perfect. Place the timer switch in the middle position at the time you always want them to cone on. I did 5 pm and they turn off at 11. Whatever time you turn the switch is the time the timer will use. They give a perfect light and look great. Very easy to assemble I put a piece of tape across the battery pack at the back because one was loose.

I have a small bathroom which had no place to plug in a night light. This suited my purpose perfectly! I set one of them on timer mode which comes on at bedtime and shuts off in the early hours; the other one I put in the hallway and did the same thing. Runs off batteries which saves on my electrical bills and the timer feature is a plus. With the low voltage on the mini lights I won't have to replace the batteries for months. It looks decorative with the silk flowers and the twinkle in the jar looks like fireflies. Great idea, great product and great price! love love love this.

Easy to put together, love the rustic wood and mason jar. Lights are adorable. I put in kitchen beside our table and now I feel I am eating in a bistro every night. You need to put 3 batters in each (double A) but there is a timer on them so they go off automatically after 6 hours. I put them on at 5 when we have dinner then they go off at 11 when we go to bed. Perfect. You can also manually turn them off and on as well. Love them.
These are the cutest lights ever. They add such a nice glow to my room, they come with a remote for light settings and I’m obsessed! Highly recommend
